Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{title}Reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking. Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you use to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try some.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to cook for Judy every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I took an even more expensive pot down from the shelf,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I handed him a fifty dollar bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The face the shopkeeper made was hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean you want to train that girl into a hitman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how to use a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do I feel lucky? Well, do ya, punk?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an Eastwood reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being serious here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this is related to avenging Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me make it clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five million isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you only need a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could make it even by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become my assistant in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I'm going to become Phantom's assistant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so if I become your assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to see the moment when Judy gets avenged with my own eyes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, there's something you need to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? A new gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go buy some tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mission today is to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's so boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work is supposed to be boring and not enjoyable at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be a good girl and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five million were stolen and four men were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it was in your territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you're not going to apologize or compensate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I offer my condolences for the deceased ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we're not going to shoulder any responsibilities for incidents that occurred before our deal was completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muroto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's true that our business has been interfered with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do whatever we can to find out who was behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll be able to take back the money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's included too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you will stay in Los Angeles until the conclusion is reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we can guarantee you a pleasant stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But originally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our money was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our men were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt we'd be able to go back to Japan empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiga, let's extend our vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to explain this to the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say we're not acclimatized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one behind this is Isaac Wisemel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisemel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no evidence that the details of our deal got leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was done by someone from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Wisemel is also a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would think that he'd start trouble in his own yard for a measly five million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He planned it out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisemel's goal is to stop the\NGodoh Group from joining Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably doesn't want to see me gain such a huge backing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too coercive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he became an executive with his rude mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the type of guy who forces things when it's needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll definitely target the Godoh Group again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just ask them to go back to Japan-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be troublesome without bait, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fishing for a shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godoh Group is the bait, and you're the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it turns out we have to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need you to stay with us for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a backup plan in case something happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the pointless talk for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wine is losing its taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you have an enjoyable vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found a coordinator that has no link with Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Giuseppe guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he really knows everything about the underworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's pointless to plan the whole thing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gift from Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This booze is thirty years old, Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll drink with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bait, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was OK at the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't say that out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is this part of the pleasant stay you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant it when I said "I can't go back empty-handed".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you have dissatisfied subordinates though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Shiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just voicing some ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should worry about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been going well recently, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what country you're in,\Ntrying to live in the underground is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3000 people of the Godoh Group will be protecting you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I have a lot I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me to pick one, I don't know which one to pick...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pick the one you want most.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want all the clothes here equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just picked one, I'd have to give up the others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the only chance that you'll get to shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you here again if there's something else you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so pick a set of clothes you want to wear today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to tell you, we won't be coming here every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, is it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it looks really good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time wearing such light clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A SIG Sauer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:12:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as the Beretta you're using now. 9mm, 15 shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this one has a smaller build,\Nsince you said she hasn't used a gun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you came here just to give me a gun I never asked you for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl Cal was mentioned in today's executive meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Wisemel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even worse, McGuire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wants to see how much she's grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least teach her how to use a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you changed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those clothes are for going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is enough to wear inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll begin firearms training now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the training ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a lonely place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it properly with the right amount of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right hand out and left hand supporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the sight to aim at the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are shaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your fingers, not your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull the trigger slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rushed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it slower, like you're squeezing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit it! I hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that, Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try reloading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her reloading is cautious and well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, try practicing by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lonely place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking to, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dead. {someone check real quotes from Taxi Driver}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:15:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, um... That was a De Niro reference...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that De Niro or whatever reference again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the dialog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, don't shoot immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike your pose, stop for one beat, and then shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to fish for the shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godohs are tired of sitting and waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They plan on going out and having some fun tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mission is to watch over them and catch Wisemel in the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even close...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How easygoing can they get?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today isn't my lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get the Goddess of Victory if you don't have confidence. {get?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's already opened up for you,\Nso what's the point of me trying to get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only thing that won't betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink {\i1}too{\i0} much now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't they act like Japanese and stay together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does the mafia really control this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a De Niro movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is probably a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But should I let her walk the same path as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should set her free as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go play poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend was supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Japanese guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like he returned to his room with a young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it can't be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was killed by me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
